覽她們的落差吧！"},{"pid":"91520efb1a19f87bb2e2706eeb27f31069b62944","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"【武漢驚爆SARS？】台灣疾管署：所有武漢入境航班 必須被登機檢疫<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191231/60437296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191231%2F60437296&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=e7cdbac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191231%2F60437296&h=90fc9b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191231/60437296</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><br />\n香港呢屌</span></span>"},{"pid":"8a8e4e87045df35efab0e3d730fda8db30cbfe5a","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:46:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba68b635a98cbf0a9fd689fe0370d5a491181ae8","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"做好文宣周街痴 AIRDROP"},{"pid":"689643b7d83af609dcb7773bc41dd29e52fc84d2","tid":1807194,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:48:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"35d8b09f6c667467cb5d661cca72a2c1125b93d3","tid":1807194,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:51:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c00f386bfd81c773c5b1fcaad88fabb304c1e937","tid":1807194,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"39f7374886676a8f15f39d327180828c952928fe","tid":1807194,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbb5c918142b89dce923dc9def4cb0a84499686b","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b303d3e6826907811f5e27c8b346753130bcc2a8","tid":1807194,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:37:19.000Z","msg":"第一張圖咩節目"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T16:42:43.000Z","msg":"富士電視台在2月3日播出的《summers的神疑問》節目中，路上隨機找了100位口罩女孩，看看她們戴上口罩和脫下口罩之後，是否真的有很大差別，而當中有45位答應拿下口罩，讓我們一覽她們的落差吧！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SMbXD53.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSMbXD53.gif&h=6306922c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61c9d465562b0e7e6c02e5bd515cba47f8262373","tid":1807194,"uid":8858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"外科口罩擋得六七成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要有震懾作用係要戴N95<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653e6a221da83f0a2f82e38c5a775388cf514dcc","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61c9d465562b0e7e6c02e5bd515cba47f8262373","tid":1807194,"uid":8858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:12:01.000Z","msg":"外科口罩擋得六七成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要有震懾作用係要戴N95<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b31829bca03188164aa8c57b4ac8a6db745ff619","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd1a9b406c2744b9af82d57e2b7e43f9c24d0b7","tid":1807194,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:47:41.000Z","msg":"【爆發肺炎的武漢海鮮市場休市整頓】<br />\n【記者放蛇發現市場內曾賣野味】<br />\n<br />\n爆發病毒性肺炎的湖北武漢華南海鮮市場周三開始休市整頓，商戶在管理部門的監督下撤離，公告指開市時間將另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n有內地傳媒在周二下午走訪海鮮市場，發現市場衛生環境惡劣，動物內臟隨地丟，有檔主透露市場本來有幾檔賣野味：「兔子、野雞、土撥鼠、蛇甚麼都有，有賣的都關門了現在。不讓賣的東西他們都放在裡面，外面不放。」<br />\n<br />\n記者嘗試向現場的調查人員詢問非法販賣野味的情況，但對方拒絕回應。<br />\n<br />\n據報，肺炎患者大部分都是海鮮市場的檔主，有醫院負責人指不排除是由魚將病菌傳播到人身上。但武漢大學醫學部一個病毒專家就說，很難想象肺炎病毒會來自海鮮市場，因肺炎病原體很少出現於海鮮中，多數都於野生動物當中找到。<br />\n<br />\n#武漢<br />\n#肺炎<br />\n#野味<br />\n#有線中國組<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1bMGJ0xAFwR0WoaV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1bMGJ0xAFwR0WoaV&d=navV%2BA4%2FMRIetR8KyPOOAM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=345a2f30\" target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1bMGJ0xAFwR0WoaV</a>"},{"pid":"98b3c6e39c80c76b22eeca1258d53f2c9473035c","tid":1807194,"uid":315626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T17:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BnEBUSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBnEBUSP.jpg&h=665cf2dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"202775a610257a53434564337bcca677224699d9","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff83b5bc475d14f9d9e9a7905d10b2dddb1c594","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T01:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863f4996dd7c6bd02d49cd089b31cad217844f87","tid":1807194,"uid":156936,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"今時今日 香港最多就係口罩<br />\n最好整啲文宣 話大陸人帶口罩就係撐香港獨立<br />\n等佢地死快啲唔該"},{"pid":"324ce2955bda88cba71a03cdd266d26c634ff001","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T02:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98904503e0df59b871818e84e92b3f19b134cf3e","tid":1807194,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"863f4996dd7c6bd02d49cd089b31cad217844f87","tid":1807194,"uid":156936,"like":11,"dislike":0,"sc